'''潘傑希爾省'''（{{lang-fa|د پنجشير ولايت}}，[[英文|英文]]: Panjshir，字面意思為「五獅之省」）位於[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]中部偏北，與[[巴達赫尚省|巴達赫尚省]]、[[巴格蘭省|巴格蘭省]]、[[努爾斯坦省|努爾斯坦省]]、[[卡比薩省|卡比薩省]]、[[拉格曼省|拉格曼省]]、[[帕爾旺省|帕爾旺省]]、[[塔哈爾省|塔哈爾省]]等省份相鄰，总面积3,610平方公里。潘傑希爾省成立于2004年4月，下辖7个[[县|县]]，省會[[巴薩拉克|巴薩拉克]]市。

在[[2021年塔利班攻勢|2021年塔利班攻勢]]中，潘傑希爾省、[[巴格蘭省|巴格蘭省]]以及[[帕爾旺省|帕爾旺省]]是全國少數沒被[[塔利班|塔利班]]直接攻陷的地區；2021年8月，塔利班重新控制阿富汗大部後，阿富汗副總統[[阿姆魯拉·薩利赫|阿姆魯拉·薩利赫]]率國民軍殘部退守潘傑希爾山谷組織[[阿富汗全國抵抗陣線|抵抗運動]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Panjshir Valley: what is the main bastion of resistance against the Taliban advance in Afghanistan|url=https://marketresearchtelecast.com/the-panjshir-valley-what-is-the-main-bastion-of-resistance-against-the-taliban-advance-in-afghanistan/131364/|date=17 August 2021|publisher=Market Research Telecast|access-date=2021-09-07|archive-date=2021-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210816202703/https://marketresearchtelecast.com/the-panjshir-valley-what-is-the-main-bastion-of-resistance-against-the-taliban-advance-in-afghanistan/131364/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=As Taliban takes over, one Afghan province is still standing strong - Here's the story of Ahmad Shah Massoud and his bastion Panjshir|url=https://www.freepressjournal.in/india/as-taliban-takes-over-one-afghan-province-is-still-standing-strong-heres-the-story-of-ahmad-shah-massoud-and-his-bastion-panjshir|access-date=2021-08-17|work=Free Press Journal|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211107181511/https://www.freepressjournal.in/india/as-taliban-takes-over-one-afghan-province-is-still-standing-strong-heres-the-story-of-ahmad-shah-massoud-and-his-bastion-panjshir|dead-url=no}}</ref>

